== user ==
drop <password>
login / identify / id <username> <password>
register <username> <password> [contact]

== vhost ==
host on
host off
host request <vhost>
host offer <vhost>
host list / host ls
host take <vhost>
host give <username> <vhost>

== memo ==
memo send <username> <message>
memo read {x-y,z|"all"|"unread"}
memo delete {x-y,z|"all"|"read"}

== set ==
set notice [on|off]
set contact [info]
set password <password> <new password>
set maxmemos [amount]
set memofwd [e-mail]

== allow ==
allow add host <hostmask>
allow add certfp [fingerprint]
allow add otrfp [fingerprint]
allow del <host|certfp|otrfp> <index>
allow list [host|certfp|otrfp]
allow plain [on|off]

== oper ==
drop <username> [permanent]
freeze <username>
list
reset password <username>
wall <message>